Where to Watch

A jive-talkin', lady-lovin' spy (Mike Myers) from the groovy 1960s is awakened from a cryogenic sleep in 1997 to help the British government find the recently thawed Dr. Evil (also Myers). With a gorgeous new partner (Elizabeth Hurley) in tow, he embarks on a quest to conquer Evil while trying to adjust to life in the '90s. Elizabeth Hurley, Seth Green, Carrie Fisher, Robert Wagner.
